Format: Verse
By: Hafiz
Title: Tell Me of Another World
Description: April 16
---
“Tell me of another world,” the broken heart says, “one where love is
never sad it loved, and the word sorry never comes to mind.”

“Show me dear God, that anything I have ever wept for will return,
will reside, in my arms.”
